Moodboard Tagreader
===================

Program for reading and saving the tags


Setup
-----
- Install the phidget libraries by following their directions. http://www.phidgets.com/docs/Operating_System_Support
- Edit the first lines of code underneath the includes in such a way that the RFID serial number matches the corresponding emotion.
- Compile the code using your choose of C++ compiler.
- Run the code as administrator

Using the program
-----------------
- Wait until the program has detected all 3 scanners.
- Press "enter" to start scanning.
- First scan a teacher tag.
- Start scanning all other tags.
- Scan the teacher tag again to quit the program and save the tags in "scannedTags.txt". 

